Configure your team's basic information and manage team lifecycle.

## Accessing Team Settings

1. Ensure you're in your team account
1. Click **Settings** in the sidebar
1. The URL is `https://sellfaster.euhome/[team]/settings`

> **Note:** Access to team settings requires the `settings.manage` permission, which is granted to team owners.

## Team Information

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Goldenhunter1206/sellfaster_content/main/public/site/images/user-guide/team-administration/team-settings/image.png)

### Team Logo

Upload or change your team's logo:

1. Click the current logo/placeholder
1. Click **Upload**
1. Select an image file
1. Save

The logo is stored in Supabase storage and appears in the account switcher and team pages.

### Team Name

Update your team's name:

1. Find the **Team Name** field
1. Enter the new name
1. Click **Save**

The team name appears:

- In the account switcher
- On team pages
- In notifications

